maml:description.maml:para: Encodes strings for use in configurations.
The configurations require some strings to be encoded for them to be imported.

command:example.dev:code: PS C:\> ConvertTo-VeeamEncodedString 'MyPlainTextPassword'

dev:remarks.maml:para: Will return an encoded string you can use in a Veeam Agent configuration file.
